description:
The Man With A Gun

On the evening of March 7th, 1927, five tough hoodlums shoved their way into the accounting office of the subway system of a large Midwest City, held two accountants and a gun-point, and robbed the safe of over fourteen thousand dollars in currency collected from various stations! It was the Tony Viaglio Gang... every man vicious, brutal, and dangerous...

Have You Seen Joe Smith?

Trying to find a man in the underworld is like stirring a sleeping lion... you can wind up dead!

Hot-Rod Trial (Text-Only Story)

Breakdown!

Police Inspector frawly couldn't get a confession from a man he knew was a killer, until some cheap hardware supplied the bait for a pitfall!

Gangs Roam The Streets

Anton Masey ran one of the big outfits manufacturing "Needle" beer in the city! Ambitious and greedy, he schemed to eliminate his rivals...
